Docker installation on Amazon linux machine
switch to root user
  sudo su -
first update the machine
  yum update -y

install docker using amazon-linux-extras package
    amazon-linux-extras install docker
    
    
to enable docker
    systemctl enable docker
to check the status of docker
  systemctl status docker
  
to start the docker service

    systemctl start docker


terraform installtion on ubuntu 20.04

tflint installtion
step-1 :  wget https://github.com/terraform-linters/tflint/releases/download/v0.47.0/tflint_linux_amd64.zip
step-2:  unzip tflint_linux_amd64.zip
step-3: mv tflint tflint_linux_amd64.zip /usr/local/bin
step-4: tflint --init
